Someone who says what we did in Afghanistan was bad and uses it to potray us as some world Imperialist Dictator....   If you feel that way, don't post about it here... go to NYC, stand at ground zero, and tell it to the people rebuilding there.  I like how no anti-war protester ever had the balls to go to the recovery site and protest.  <br>
<br>
OR... someone who says that actions after 9-11 was ok, but only until somethign worse happens should we take any means to actually protect ourselves further.  Next time some terrorists blow, poison, or irradiate something here, and we get another few thousand dead, and the perpetrators are AGAIN linked to Iraq if they aren't Iraq directly next time.... are you gonna stick to your guns and say the dead were worth it?  That they were &quot;necessary&quot; for things to come to a head?<br>
